reviewText: My 1 year old son absolutely loves this video! The characters are a little goofy and dated, but he doesn't know that! There are lots of kids and adults singing and dancing, and he imitates them all! He tries to snap his fingers whenever anyone mentions the "mosquito song" and he has been doing this for at least three months! It is our late-afternoon-I-can't-take-it-anymore solution! the entire 55 minutes hold his attention, too.
